item.title: Bio
item.description: My name is (William) Ryan Parker. I typically go by my middle name, Ryan. I currently run a software engineering group at Indeed specializing in full-stack engineering for financial products. I received my undergraduate degree from the University of Central Arkanas, majoring in Chemistry and minoring in Computer Science. I obtained my master’s degree from the Brodbelt group at the University of Texas at Austin. There my work focused on identification of cystiene-containing peptides and proteins via chemical derivitaziation of chromophores.
